back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104icm1665703229996.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/icm1665703229996.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/icm1665703229996.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"icm1665703229996\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify a translation table for input characters.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"icm1665703229996__topic_d140819e1_d140820e1_d140821e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"icm1665703229996__p_d140822e1_d140823e1_d140824e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$KEYBOARD</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyboardTranslationTable</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"icm1665703229996__section_uc3_kvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d150166e65\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"icm1665703229996__table_d16646e1_d16647e1_d16648e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">client assignment files</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"icm1665703229996__section_k5l_kvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d150166e111\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"icm1665703229996__p_d140831e1_d140832e1_d140833e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$KEYBOARD</span> causes the <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyboardTranslationTable</var>\n        specified under the current library to be loaded.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"icm1665703229996__p_d140834e1_d140835e1_d140836e1\">In character mode (CHUI), the translation table\n        specified by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$KEYBOARD</span> is used for all the entered characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"icm1665703229996__p_d140837e1_d140838e1_d140839e1\">In GUI mode, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$KEYBOARD</span> is used for\n        ASCII characters and Uniface control characters such as GOLD:R. Other characters are\n        accepted without translation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"icm1665703229996__p_d140840e1_d140841e1_d140842e1\">You can use the ProcScript function\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyboard</span> to test and to set the current keyboard translation table.\n        Remember that the keyboard translation table loaded depends on the library in use when the\n        application is started.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"icm1665703229996__section_isd_nvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d150166e144\">Example: $KEYBOARD</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"icm1665703229996__pre_q4k_4vx_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$KEYBOARD = NCD</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mew1705662925747.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keyboard Translation Tables</a><p>A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbn1665702665252.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyboard</a><p>Return or set the current keyboard translation table.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528474\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$KEYBOARD Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify a translation table for input characters. $KEYBOARD { = } KeyboardTranslationTable Defaults Assignment file: client assignment files Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $KEYBOARD causes the KeyboardTranslationTable specified under the current library to be loaded. In character mode (CHUI), the translation table specified by $KEYBOARD is used for all the entered characters. In GUI mode, $KEYBOARD is used for ASCII characters and Uniface control characters such as GOLD:R. Other characters are accepted without translation. You can use the ProcScript function $keyboard to test and to set the current keyboard translation table. Remember that the keyboard translation table loaded depends on the library in use when the application is started. Example: $KEYBOARD $KEYBOARD = NCD Copy Related Links Keyboard Translation Tables A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface. $keyboard Return or set the current keyboard translation table. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}